Jonas Buhl Bjerre vs Magnus Carlsen
Energi Danmark Champions Battle 2019 round 02, May-22
Ruy Lopez (C60)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 g6 5. O-O Bg7 6. c3 d6 7. d4 Bd7 8. Re1 Nge7 9. d5 Nb8 10. Bxd7+ Nxd7 11. c4 h6 12. Nc3 O-O 13. Rb1 f5 14. b4 Nf6 15. Nd2 c6 16. Bb2 Rc8 17.
